《'''罪夜之奔'''》（{{lang-en|''The Night Of''}}）是一部[[美國|美國]]、[[英國|英國]]共同製作，由[[HBO|HBO]]及[[BBC_Worldwide|BBC Worldwide]]播出、共有8集的[[犯罪片|犯罪片]][[迷你劇|迷你]][[電視影集|電視影集]]。本作是2008–2009年英國電視影集《[[司法正義|司法正義]]》的[[重製|翻拍版]]。<ref name="turturro">{{en}}{{cite news |last=Andreeva |first=Nellie |title=John Turturro To Replace Robert De Niro As James Gandolfini's Successor In HBO Mini 'Criminal Justice' |url=http://deadline.com/2014/04/john-turturro-to-replace-robert-de-niro-as-james-gandolfinis-successor-in-hbo-mini-criminal-justice-717631/ |accessdate=2014-08-12 |publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |date=2014-04-21 |archive-date=2018-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180616053533/https://deadline.com/2014/04/john-turturro-to-replace-robert-de-niro-as-james-gandolfinis-successor-in-hbo-mini-criminal-justice-717631/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>這部影集的故事由{{tsl|en|Richard Price (writer)|理查德·普莱斯}}和{{tsl|en|Steven Zaillian|史蒂芬·柴里安}}兩人共同編寫，而柴里安同時也擔任了影集中大多集數的導演。<ref name="order">{{en}}{{cite news |last=Andreeva |first=Nellie |title=Quartet Cast In HBO's 'Crime' Miniseries |url=http://deadline.com/2014/10/hbo-crime-criminal-justice-cast-james-gandolfini-857801/ |accessdate=2014-10-22 |publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |date=2014-10-22 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124020723/https://deadline.com/2014/10/hbo-crime-criminal-justice-cast-james-gandolfini-857801/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2016年7月10日首播<ref name="premiere">{{en}}{{cite news|last=Petski|first=Denise|title=James Gandolfini's Passion Project 'Criminal Justice' Gets Summer Premiere On HBO As 'The Night Of'|url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/james-gandolfini-criminal-justice-hbo-the-night-of-hbo-summer-premiere-1201718731/|accessdate=2016-03-11|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2016-03-11|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118120759/https://deadline.com/2016/03/james-gandolfini-criminal-justice-hbo-the-night-of-hbo-summer-premiere-1201718731/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news|last1=Pederson|first1=Erik|url=http://deadline.com/2016/04/hbo-premiere-dates-ballers-vice-principals-the-night-of-1201740255/|title=HBO Books Summer Dates For 'Ballers', 'Vice Principals' & 'The Night Of'|date=2016-04-19|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|accessdate=2016-04-20|archive-date=2018-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180616103334/https://deadline.com/2016/04/hbo-premiere-dates-ballers-vice-principals-the-night-of-1201740255/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其中第一集則在三週前的6月24日透過HBO [[隨選視訊|On Demand]]提前播映。<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2016/06/22/the-night-of-first-part-available-this-friday-june-24-on-hbo-now-hbo-go-hbo-on-demand-affiliate-portals-188300/20160622hbo01/|title="The Night Of": First Part Available This Friday, June 24 on HBO NOW, HBO GO, HBO On Demand, Affiliate Portals|publisher=[[The_Futon_Critic|The Futon Critic]]|date=2016-06-22|access-date=2016-06-25|archive-date=2020-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200617224651/http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2016/06/22/the-night-of-first-part-available-this-friday-june-24-on-hbo-now-hbo-go-hbo-on-demand-affiliate-portals-188300/20160622hbo01/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

